main event: The witness reported seeing a swift, fast-moving white object about three times the size of an automobile, flying at an estimated speed of 3,000 miles per hour and an altitude of 500 to 1,500 feet.
interesting points: The object changed color as it approached the witness.
The witness felt a sense of great magnitude and that time seemed to stand still.
The witness is unsure if they actually saw something, but considers it to be a mysterious sighting.
The witness requests a reply and assistance in determining what they may have seen.
